commitResults.messageBody:
Input most typical user commands into the input.txt file and ran
runtest.bat. Fixed certain new line issues inside chatbot code to remove
awkward spacing.

Fulfilled minimal and typical testing requirements. Script will be used
to test for future stretch goals.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add comphrensive error handling for invalid inputs
commitResults.messageBody:
- Empty task descriptions for TODO, DEADLINE, EVENT
- Unknown task types
- DEADLINE tasks missing /by date
- EVENT tasks missing /from or /to time
- mark/unmark commands with missing or invalid task numbers

Provides clear user feedback on invalid commands and improves robustness and prevents incorrect task creation

commitResults.messageTitle: Add support for deleting tasks from list
commitResults.messageBody:
Convert normal Task array to ArrayList from java Collections in order to
ensure ease of adding and deleting / resizing of ArrayList.

Tested with Automated I/O redirection script to ensure that delete is
working as intended.

Change from String to Date, Time and DateTime
commitResults.messageBody:
For deadline task, parse date String to Date object.
For event task, parse from datetime String to DateTime object.
For event task, also parse to time String to Time object, then store as
DateTime object (assuming event always ends on the same day as event
start day).
